@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the class "Plane"

[*] --> Order : «M» Plane Acquired/
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance

Order --> Arrival : «M» Plane Arrived/
Arrival --> Preparation : «M» Plane Prepared/

Preparation --> Operations : «M» Plane Ready for Operations/
Operations --> Maintenance : «M» No Scheduled Flights or Maintenance Required/
Maintenance --> Preparation : «M» Plane Serviced and Ready for Operations/

Order --> [*] : «M» Plane Permanently Withdrawn from Service/
Arrival --> [*] : «M» Plane No Longer Available for Use/
Preparation --> [*] : «M» Plane Condition Unknown/
Operations --> [*] : «M» Plane Scheduled Flights Unknown/
Maintenance --> [*] : «M» Plane Serviced and Ready for Operations/

@enduml
